summary: Lore-friendly teleporter from Riften to Dayspring Canyon (Fort Dawnguard)
descriptionHtml:
Description:
Near the Riften south gate you can find teleport stone to Dayspring Canyon (Fort Dawnguard). During the Second Era this stone was used by Jarl of Riften to visit his vampire son. And now you can use this ancient way to have a quick access to Fort Dawnguard.

This mod will be useful for those who avoid to use fast travel but hate run to Fort Dawnguard for hundred times. And now you can travel to Riften by carriage and then use stone to teleport to Fort Danguard. Have fun!

Installation:
Use NMM or manually place .esp file into skyrim data folder
author: Zenkiki
